tasks.instruction: Analyze the uploaded PDF file at /workspace/uploads/DashGenius - Personalized Dashboard.pdf to understand the design requirements and extract key visual elements, layout structure, color scheme, and UI components that should be implemented for the Digital Guidance Platform front page.

Update the Digital Guidance Platform front page design based on the design analysis report at /workspace/digital_guidance_platform/docs/design_analysis.md. Implement the modern dashboard-style layout, color scheme, and UI components as specified in the analysis to match the DashGenius design reference.
